name: CoreAPI Tools_BG_CreateJob
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Tools-Background-Jobs
about:
Description

Planet 9-API Tools_BG_CreateJob maintains the Background Jobs list.

API Tools_BG_CreateJob is the API to access the Planet 9 Background Jobs and performs the REST operations performed for the background jobs.

Operations Performed

Get

Get the selected Background Job

RequestID
ResponseGet- Definition                          

List

Get the list of Background Jobs. List contains the scheduler, Javascript_group and JSclass details.

ResponseList(array)- Definition           

Delete

Delete the Background Job

RequestID                                 

Save

Save or create the new job

RequestSave(object)-Definition
